煌びやかな衣装となっているんですけど
it's quite a gorgeous outfit,

348
00:27:40,879 --> 00:27:43,879
ちょっと今、スクショタイム撮る？
Wanna take some screenshots now?

349
00:27:43,879 --> 00:27:45,879
イェーイ！
Yay!

350
00:27:45,879 --> 00:27:47,879
可愛いですか？
Is it cute?

351
00:27:47,879 --> 00:27:51,879
ぜひあの、ハッシュタグでね、
Please, using the hashtag,

352
00:27:51,879 --> 00:27:54,379
ぜひ呟いてください。
please tweet about it.

353
00:27:54,379 --> 00:27:55,879
可愛いでしょ？
It's cute, right?

354
00:27:55,879 --> 00:27:58,879
何やらね、この後ちょっと衣装のいろいろ
Apparently, later on, about the outfit details...

355
00:27:58,879 --> 00:28:01,879
細部までちょっと見る機会がありそうな
I feel like there might be a chance to see the details,

356
00:28:01,879 --> 00:28:03,879
予感がするので、
so for now,

357
00:28:03,879 --> 00:28:06,879
一旦スクショだけお願いします！
just some screenshots, please!

358
00:28:06,879 --> 00:28:09,879
そして、あとこちらね、見て！
And also, look at this!

359
00:28:09,879 --> 00:28:12,879
手首にプラプラって紐があるんだけど
There are these dangling strings on the wrists,

360
00:28:12,879 --> 00:28:15,879
これね、取れます！
but these can be removed!

361
00:28:15,879 --> 00:28:17,879
じゃ、取ってもらおうかな？
So, shall I have them taken off?

362
00:28:17,879 --> 00:28:19,879
えいっ！えいっ！
Ei! Ei!

363
00:28:19,879 --> 00:28:22,879
ということで、はい、取れまーす。
And so, yes, they come off.

364
00:28:22,879 --> 00:28:25,879
こちらバージョンもスクショ撮ってもらおう。
Let's have some screenshots of this version too.

365
00:28:25,879 --> 00:28:27,879
ヘイ！
Hey!

366
00:28:27,879 --> 00:28:30,379
可愛いですか？
Is it cute?

367
00:28:30,379 --> 00:28:32,879
ぴゃ〜！
Pya~!

368
00:28:32,879 --> 00:28:35,879
ね、すごい可愛らしい衣装。
Right? A very lovely outfit.

369
00:28:35,879 --> 00:28:38,879
ちょっとね、あの、ドキドキするんですが、
I'm a bit, um, nervous, but...

370
00:28:38,879 --> 00:28:40,879
うん。
Yeah.

371
00:28:40,879 --> 00:28:43,879
いや〜、なんか、でもちょっと一人寂しいな。
Man... but it feels a bit lonely all by myself.

372
00:28:43,879 --> 00:28:45,879
なんか、ダインさん...
I wonder, Dain-san...

373
00:28:46,279 --> 00:28:48,179
あ！いた可愛い！
Ah! There he is, cute!

374
00:28:48,179 --> 00:28:50,279
ね、なんか、モゾモゾしてる。
Look, he's squirming around.

375
00:28:50,279 --> 00:28:51,379
お、どうしたどうした？
Oh, what's wrong?

376
00:28:51,379 --> 00:28:52,879
うわぁ〜！
Uwaa~!

377
00:28:52,879 --> 00:28:55,379
ダインさん飛んできた！
Dain-san flew over!

378
00:28:55,379 --> 00:28:58,179
そんなにノエちゃんに会いたかったんかな？
Did you want to see Noe-chan that much?

379
00:28:58,179 --> 00:29:00,279
可愛いね〜。
So cute.

380
00:29:00,279 --> 00:29:01,879
いっぱいスクショ撮れた？
Did you get lots of screenshots?

381
00:29:01,879 --> 00:29:04,879
ダインさんとのツーショット！
A two-shot with Dain-san!

382
00:29:04,879 --> 00:29:06,379
可愛い。え？何々？
Cute. Eh? What is it?

383
00:29:06,379 --> 00:29:09,879
あ、今日は安眠テーマで、あ、心地がいい。
Ah, with today's sleep theme, it's comfortable.

384
00:29:09,879 --> 00:29:11,379
あ、なるほどね。
Ah, I see.

385
00:29:11,379 --> 00:29:13,379
ん？曲のリクエスト？
Hm? A song request?

386
00:29:13,379 --> 00:29:16,379
あ、子守唄みたいな曲が聴きたい。
Ah, you want to hear a lullaby-like song.

387
00:29:16,379 --> 00:29:18,379
あ、そうなの？ダインさん。
Oh, really? Dain-san.

388
00:29:18,379 --> 00:29:21,379
じゃあせっかくね、ダインさん来てくれたし、
Well, since Dain-san came all this way,

389
00:29:21,379 --> 00:29:23,879
一緒に、じゃ、子守唄...
let's sing a lullaby together...

390
00:29:23,879 --> 00:29:26,879
うん。歌うよ！歌う。
Yeah. I'll sing! I will.

391
00:29:26,879 --> 00:29:29,379
だからちょっとついてきて。
So come with me for a bit.

392
00:29:29,379 --> 00:29:31,379
一緒に行くよ。
Let's go together.

393
00:29:31,379 --> 00:29:32,879
ほら、おいで！
Come on, over here!

394
00:29:35,879 --> 00:29:41,879
ぼうやの夢よ
Little boy's dream...

395
00:29:42,079 --> 00:29:48,179
小さな人の子よ
O little child of man,

396
00:29:48,179 --> 00:29:55,379
森へ迷い込んだ
who wandered into the forest.

397
00:29:55,879 --> 00:29:59,879
大きな...
A big...

398
00:30:00,798 --> 00:30:02,798
空の羽が
The wings of the sky...

399
00:30:02,798 --> 00:30:09,298
ぼうやは見えないのね
...you cannot see them, can you, little one?

400
00:30:09,798 --> 00:30:16,598
何も知らないまるいほっぺよ
Round cheeks that know nothing of the world.

401
00:30:23,798 --> 00:30:29,798
眠れや眠れ
Sleep, oh sleep,

402
00:30:30,598 --> 00:30:36,598
静かな水辺においで
Come to the quiet water's edge.

403
00:30:37,498 --> 00:30:43,898
ぼうやの夢は
The little one's dreams...

404
00:30:44,398 --> 00:30:50,698
竜の背に運ばれて
...are carried on the back of a dragon...

405
00:30:51,298 --> 00:30:56,698
山の向こうへ消える
...and vanish beyond the mountains.

406
00:31:14,798 --> 00:31:21,198
よろずの子も並んで眠る
All the children of the world sleep side by side.

407
00:31:29,198 --> 00:31:34,598
七つ数えたら
Once you count to seven,

408
00:31:35,098 --> 00:31:42,698
仲よく眠って来る
everyone will fall into a peaceful slumber.

409
00:31:47,498 --> 00:31:53,498
何も見えない
Seeing nothing,

410
00:31:53,898 --> 00:32:00,198
小さなおめめよ
those tiny little eyes.

411
00:32:00,798 --> 00:32:06,798
眠れや眠れ
Sleep, oh sleep,

412
00:32:07,598 --> 00:32:13,798
そよぐ草むらにおいで
Come to the swaying grass fields.

413
00:32:14,598 --> 00:32:21,098
ぼうやの夢は
The little one's dreams...

414
00:32:23,098 --> 00:32:29,098
母さんを探しては
...search for their mother...

415
00:32:29,598 --> 00:32:35,598
空の向こうへ帰る
...and return to the far side of the sky.

416
00:32:36,798 --> 00:32:42,998
竜の背に運ばれて
Carried on the back of a dragon,

417
00:32:43,798 --> 00:32:50,298
山の向こうへ消える
they vanish beyond the mountains.

418
00:33:06,998 --> 00:33:11,998
プラネタリウム
作詞・作曲：愛
Planetarium
Lyrics & Composition: Ai

419
00:33:31,598 --> 00:33:35,098
夕月夜 顔だす 消えてく
The evening moon peeks out, as they fade away—

420
00:33:35,098 --> 00:33:41,098
子供の声
the voices of children.

421
00:33:41,598 --> 00:33:45,098
遠く遠く
Far, far away,

422
00:33:45,098 --> 00:33:51,098
この空のどこかに 君はいるんだろう
somewhere in this sky, you must be there.

423
00:33:51,598 --> 00:33:58,098
夏の終わりに二人で 抜け出したこの公園で
In this park we snuck out to together at summer's end,

424
00:33:58,598 --> 00:34:04,098
あの星座 何だか 覚えてる
I somehow remember that constellation.

425
00:34:10,898 --> 00:34:14,598
会えなくても 記憶をたどって
Even if we can't meet, I trace my memories,

426
00:34:15,098 --> 00:34:19,598
同じ幸せを見たいんだ
wanting to see the same happiness.

427
00:34:20,098 --> 00:34:26,598
あの香りと共に 花火がパッと開く
Along with that scent, fireworks suddenly bloom.

428
00:34:29,398 --> 00:34:34,098
行きたいよ 君のところへ
I want to go to where you are.

429
00:34:34,598 --> 00:34:39,098
今すぐ かけだして 行きたいよ
I want to run to you right now.

430
00:34:39,598 --> 00:34:43,098
真っ暗で 何も見えない
In the pitch black where nothing can be seen,

431
00:34:43,598 --> 00:34:48,598
怖くても 大丈夫
it's okay even if it's scary.

432
00:34:49,098 --> 00:34:53,598
数えきれない星空が
The countless stars in the night sky...

433
00:34:54,098 --> 00:35:00,098
今もずっと ここにあるんだよ
...are still here, and always will be.

434
00:35:00,098 --> 00:35:05,098
泣かないよ
I won't cry.

435
00:35:01,319 --> 00:35:06,819
泣かないよ　届くだろう　きれいな空だったから
I won't cry; they'll surely reach you, since the sky was so beautiful.

436
00:35:15,619 --> 00:35:25,019
あの道まで響く靴の音が耳に残る
The sound of footsteps echoing to that road lingers in my ears.

437
00:35:25,719 --> 00:35:35,019
大きな自分の影を見つめて思うのでしょう
Gazing at my long shadow, I find myself lost in thought.

438
00:35:35,519 --> 00:35:44,419
ちっとも変わらないはずなのに　せつない気持ちふくらんでく
Though nothing should have changed, this painful feeling just keeps growing.

439
00:35:45,019 --> 00:35:53,519
どんなに想ったって君はもういない
No matter how much I think of you, you're no longer here.

440
00:35:54,019 --> 00:36:03,319
行きたいよ　君のそばに　小さくても　小さくても
I want to go to your side, even if I'm small, even if I'm small.

441
00:36:03,819 --> 00:36:13,119
1番に　君が好きだよ　強くいられる
I love you more than anyone; you're the reason I can be strong.

442
00:36:13,619 --> 00:36:23,119
願いを　流れ星に　そっと唱えてみたけれど
I tried softly whispering my wish to a shooting star, but...

443
00:36:23,519 --> 00:36:35,319
泣かないよ　届くだろう　きれいな空に
I won't cry; they'll surely reach you, in the beautiful sky.

444
00:36:50,319 --> 00:36:59,819
会えなくても記憶をたどって　同じ幸せを見たいんだ
Even if we can't meet, I'll trace my memories; I want to see that same happiness.

445
00:37:00,319 --> 00:37:08,419
あの香りと共に花火がぱっと開く
Along with that scent, the fireworks suddenly burst open.

446
00:37:09,019 --> 00:37:18,119
行きたいよ　君のところへ　小さな手をにぎりしめて
I want to go to where you are, squeezing your small hand tight.

447
00:37:18,719 --> 00:37:28,119
泣きたいよ　それはそれはきれいな空だった
I want to cry; it was such a very, very beautiful sky.

448
00:37:28,519 --> 00:37:37,919
願いを　流れ星に　そっと唱えてみたけれど
I tried softly whispering my wish to a shooting star, but...

449
00:37:38,319 --> 00:37:55,319
泣きたいよ　届かない想いをこの空に...
I want to cry; sending these unreachable feelings into this sky...

450
00:39:05,319 --> 00:39:10,119
もう何十回もう何百回も　震むソラ見上げて
Dozens, hundreds of times, looking up at the blurred sky.

451
00:39:10,519 --> 00:39:14,919
辿り着いた場所が　運命のダイヤモンド
The place I finally reached is the diamond of fate.

452
00:39:15,319 --> 00:39:20,319
何千回もう何万回も　涙流したきみへ
To you, who has shed tears thousands, tens of thousands of times.

453
00:39:20,819 --> 00:39:24,919
ねえ諦められたことはあったっけ？
Hey, was there ever anything you truly gave up on?

454
00:39:25,319 --> 00:39:30,319
「憧れ＝限界」だから　もういらないよ
Because 'Admiration = Limit,' I don't need it anymore.

455
00:39:30,819 --> 00:39:35,319
そこに留まるなんて　もったいないでしょ
Just staying there would be such a waste, wouldn't it?

456
00:39:35,819 --> 00:39:41,319
それぞれの物語　交差する瞬間を
The moments where our individual stories intersect.

457
00:39:41,319 --> 00:39:47,319
見つめる意味は
The meaning of gazing upon them is...

458
00:39:47,819 --> 00:39:52,619
放った夢だけ　大きな弧を描いて
Only the dreams we released draw a great arc.

459
00:39:53,119 --> 00:40:01,319
はちきれそうな煌めきを　消えることなく　どこまででも
A brilliance about to burst, never fading, going anywhere and everywhere.

460
00:40:02,479 --> 00:40:05,279
世界の向こうに 届けよう
Let's send it to the other side of the world

461
00:40:06,079 --> 00:40:10,379
終わることのない この胸の衝動は
This never-ending impulse in my heart

462
00:40:10,579 --> 00:40:12,979
どうしたって どうしても
No matter what, no matter how

463
00:40:12,979 --> 00:40:15,379
ぼくを呼んでいた
It was calling out to me

464
00:40:15,579 --> 00:40:18,579
だから その先へと
So, towards what lies ahead

465
00:40:18,779 --> 00:40:21,579
走り続ける
I'll keep on running

466
00:40:21,879 --> 00:40:25,279
次へ 次へ
To the next, and the next

467
00:41:05,179 --> 00:41:09,179
妄想だった 中途半端な
It was a delusion, a half-baked

468
00:41:09,179 --> 00:41:14,279
不甲斐なさ抱えて 立ち尽くしていた
Helplessness that left me standing still

469
00:41:14,479 --> 00:41:15,679
通り雨はプレリュード
The passing rain is a prelude

470
00:41:15,879 --> 00:41:18,179
何千回も 何万回も
Thousands, tens of thousands of times

471
00:41:18,179 --> 00:41:20,579
挑み続けた君へ
To you who kept on trying

472
00:41:20,779 --> 00:41:24,479
ねぇ聴かせてよ「夢は叶うんだ」って
Hey, let me hear you say "dreams do come true"

473
00:41:25,879 --> 00:41:30,279
『諦め＝完敗』ならば 絶対にないよ
If "giving up = total defeat," then that's definitely not it

474
00:41:30,479 --> 00:41:34,979
だれに邪魔されようと ためらわないで
No matter who gets in your way, don't hesitate

475
00:41:35,379 --> 00:41:37,679
託された情熱を
The passion I was entrusted with

476
00:41:37,679 --> 00:41:40,379
落とさずにつないでいく
I'll pass it on without letting it go

477
00:41:40,579 --> 00:41:44,679
そう 最後まで
Yes, until the very end

478
00:41:48,179 --> 00:41:52,379
フラッグに誓い 勇ましく旗めいて
Swearing on the flag, fluttering bravely

479
00:41:52,579 --> 00:41:55,779
鳴り止まないファンファーレ
The never-ending fanfare

480
00:41:56,579 --> 00:42:01,379
いつも心に 流れていた
Was always flowing in my heart

481
00:42:01,979 --> 00:42:05,479
遠い未来へ 祈るよう
Like a prayer towards the distant future

482
00:42:05,679 --> 00:42:09,979
忘れられない あの日々の後悔を
The regrets of those unforgettable days

483
00:42:10,179 --> 00:42:16,479
追いかけて 追いかけて 滑り込んだ この想い
Chasing it, chasing it, these feelings I slid into

484
00:42:16,679 --> 00:42:21,479
青いソラに ふと溢れていった
Suddenly overflowed into the blue sky

485
00:42:21,679 --> 00:42:26,179
遠く 遠く
Far, far away

486
00:42:46,379 --> 00:42:50,179
トレビアンナイト
Trēs Bien Knight

487
00:42:53,479 --> 00:42:55,379
終わらない 終わらない
Won't end, won't end

488
00:42:55,379 --> 00:42:57,379
仕事が山積み終わらない
The pile of work just won't end

489
00:42:57,479 --> 00:42:59,279
止まらない 止まらない
Won't stop, won't stop

490
00:42:59,279 --> 00:43:01,179
それでも時間は止まらない
Even so, time won't stop

491
00:43:01,279 --> 00:43:04,679
YO! YO! ヘトヘト たまり溜まったヘイト
YO! YO! I'm exhausted, the accumulated hate

492
00:43:04,879 --> 00:43:08,579
連発お門違いバット コンボ メイス 銀座バット
Endless misplaced bats, combos, maces, Ginza bats

493
00:43:08,779 --> 00:43:12,079
Swing 今日も一杯 今日も一杯
Swing, another full day, another full day

494
00:43:12,179 --> 00:43:15,579
Found NO MORE 鞭 GIVE ME GIVE ME 汁
Found, NO MORE whip, GIVE ME GIVE ME juice

495
00:43:15,679 --> 00:43:19,079
I see 奔走 ANYTIME 奔走 ANYTIME
I see, struggling ANYTIME, struggling ANYTIME

496
00:43:19,179 --> 00:43:22,679
はぁ〜 溜め息ブレンドで エナジー空っぽだ
Sigh... an energy blend that's completely empty

497
00:43:22,879 --> 00:43:26,179
自分自身に厳しすぎちゃう
Being too hard on myself

498
00:43:26,379 --> 00:43:29,679
すぐさまヘラヘラ優等生 さっぱり足りない 順応性
Instantly a silly honor student, lacking any adaptability

499
00:43:29,879 --> 00:43:33,179
自分自身としっかり向き合う
Facing myself properly

500
00:43:33,379 --> 00:43:36,679
一番必要なものは
The thing I need most is

501
00:43:36,879 --> 00:43:40,179
トレビアン ご褒美 頂戴
Trēs Bien, give me a reward

502
00:43:40,379 --> 00:43:43,679
てんてこ舞うようなリズムにバイバイしちゃえ
Say goodbye to the frantic rhythm

503
00:43:43,879 --> 00:43:47,179
ドレミファの音にご覧
Look at the Do-Re-Mi notes

504
00:43:47,379 --> 00:43:51,879
ぎゅうぎゅうと詰め込んじゃダメ どんどんフリーダム
Don't cram it all in, getting more and more freedom

505
00:43:53,679 --> 00:43:54,679
Uh

506
00:43:57,179 --> 00:43:58,179
オーライ オーライ
Alright Alright

507
00:43:58,379 --> 00:44:02,179
好きなもの食べ放題 オキシトシン増す脳内
All-you-can-eat favorite foods, oxytocin increasing in the brain

508
00:44:02,379 --> 00:44:05,679
ほら もっともっとちょうだい 膨大
Look, give me more and more, massive amounts

509
00:44:05,879 --> 00:44:09,579
Get Ready 多忙です たまに空振り
Get Ready, I'm busy, occasionally striking out

510
00:44:09,779 --> 00:44:13,179
満ちた日こそ胸張り 大盛り
On days when I'm full, puff out my chest, extra serving

511
00:44:13,379 --> 00:44:16,679
いらない まやかしの甘い夜更かし
Don't need fake sweet late nights

512
00:44:16,879 --> 00:44:20,179
ハッピーになるため歌おう 声高らかに
Let's sing to be happy, loud and clear

513
00:44:20,379 --> 00:44:23,679
自分自身がやっぱり一番
I am, after all, the number one

514
00:44:23,879 --> 00:44:27,179
理性と欲望が平行線 望みは幸せエンドレス
Reason and desire are parallel lines, wishing for endless happiness

515
00:44:27,379 --> 00:44:30,679
自分自身としっかり向き合う
Facing myself properly

516
00:44:30,879 --> 00:44:33,679
我慢は身体に毒だよ
Endurance is poison for the body

517
00:44:33,879 --> 00:44:37,179
トレビアン ご褒美 頂戴
Trēs Bien, give me a reward

518
00:44:37,379 --> 00:44:40,679
てんてこ舞うようなリズムにバイバイしちゃえ
Say goodbye to the frantic rhythm

519
00:44:40,879 --> 00:44:44,679
ドレミファの音にご覧
Look at the Do-Re-Mi notes

